{"tid":2015871,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[一升百彈]唔該呢個時候放落兩登偏見，因為我諗到啦，我呢鋪一定做硬文才我起到頭啦","createTime":"2020-05-14T04:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T17:23:52.000Z","uid":89605,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1bb05d2212ff824bb003a801d8695c1156229c56","tid":2015871,"uid":89605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:06:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7228068/page/6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7228068%2Fpage%2F6&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=be7563b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7228068/page/6</a><br />\n基本上長篇大論，水蛇春或回文我唔睇啦<br />\n我試下了結哂你地＿<br />\n個人言論或者思想係會好清晰咁表達又或者表達得差甚至係三：越講越糊塗<br />\n可能發帖人大致上都好好清晰咁表達你既言論<br />\n不過你要知道你再發表一D諗法，係要睇有冇人BUY你參考你，甚至反駁你引起哄動<br />\n好明顯發帖人一味就批評、針對、用醜人比喻我地、眾人不知我獨知黎貶低我地<br />\n你亦犯左冇提供情報就黎針對批評他人呢個錯誤<br />\n後者我有保留，你話件事情點樣點樣我地點樣、我認為咁樣樣<br />\n但只少量情報就發表思想導致清晰度不足就明顯SHOW哂出黎<br />\n相信呢點亦係大量回覆POST既起因；EQ低玻璃心<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係一個有熱誠既人<br />\n唔該講出一個解決方案<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncome on baby，來用好評負評決定我生與死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14333d098d4d754875a7fa5c115850050460a195","tid":2015871,"uid":89605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c71be6f3bfaf5d0a9a6a1928895cbcd9a7bc712","tid":2015871,"uid":89605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:34:48.000Z","msg":"百搭文面世冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gi